Using PHP 8.3.12

To run the command line script:
php cli.php currency-layer-api-key=(key)
php cli.php currency-layer-api-ke=e5adcce0a8be7b2cd79a13f7bbf78a1b

To run the web script:
Start PHP with: 
php -S localhost:8000
Go to URL:
http://localhost:8000/



Command line script:
cli.php

Database defintion:
ddl.sql

Web page:
index.html

Web JavaScript:
webscript.js

Web PHP script:
web.php

Example Currency layer response:
currency-layer-response.json

